      • updateKeyList

        public void updateKeyList()
        method to update the keyList for the client. Key may be outdated, because a user is removed from the group, and a new key for the whole group is generated, the server will always encode any information with the most recent key. Should only be called if error occurred in decoding.

      • readResponseFromServer

        Returns:
